        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 17 at 9:27PM CDT by NWS Memphis TN</headline>
        <description>At 927 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Cottage Grove, or 11 miles west of Paris, moving northeast at 5 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 40 mph and pea size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Paris, Cottage Grove, Ore Springs, Osage, Whitlock, Jones Mill,
Porter Court, and Como.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
